Bandit - ()
- Starting from the second night, they may choose a target to pillage. This is separate to the faction kill.
- If the bandit manages to kill their target, they will gain 3000 coins. If they manage to kill a King, they will instead receive 7000 coins.
- The pillage is a strong attack and is end phase. The ability has a cooldown of 2 phases.
- Does not respawn.
